feat(agents): PATCH /admin/agents/:id/skill-attachments with slot-collision (I-P1-4)

Attach-time validation closes the I-P1-4 gap:
  - skill-not-found: attachment references an unresolved skill id
  - binding-missing: skill declares a slot the attachment doesn't bind
  - binding-orphan: attachment binds a slot the skill doesn't declare
