- Status: DONE | DONE_WITH_CONCERNS | BLOCKED | NEEDS_CONTEXT
- Commit SHAs (2)
- Test counts per file
- Confirm pnpm build (workspace-wide) is clean
- Confirm that AX_INSTALLED_SKILLS_JSON is NOT in ENV_ALLOWLIST (and no test asserts otherwise)

## Self-review

- sandbox-subprocess: zod schema added; write loop is inside the try-block so failures wrap in sandbox-prep-failed
- sandbox-subprocess: chmod 0555 happens AFTER all writes, not before
- sandbox-subprocess: skill id is regex-validated by zod AND the path uses path.join (defense in depth)
- pod-spec: env var only present when installedSkills is non-empty (no `: undefined` entries)
