- runner main: materializer called BEFORE SDK spawn AND BEFORE session.get-config (or right after — but BEFORE any SDK work)
- runner main: failure aborts with exit code 2 (matches the existing setupProxy failure path)
- installed-skills.ts: defensive shape checks at every level (typeof, Array.isArray, regex)
- installed-skills test cleans up tmpdir + restores process.env in afterEach

